@2515 = ~Mass Protection From Fire~
@2516 = ~Mass Protection From Fire (Abjuration)
Level: 5
Sphere: Protection, Elemental (fire)
Range: 30 meters
Duration: 3 rounds + 1 round/level
Casting Time: 5
Area of Effect: 9-meters radius
Saving Throw: none

When the spell is cast, it confers to the party of the preacher a complete invulnerability to normal fires (torches, bonfires, oil fires, and the like). Likewise this spell absorbs 80% of all damage done by magical fires such as fiery dragon breath, spells such as burning hands, fireball, fire seeds, fire storm, flame strike, meteor swarm, hell hound or pyrohydra breath, etc.. The preacher may cast this spell towards an area, in which case only members of parties within the area will be covered by the spell, which will ignore enemies.~
